%h2
    Password Reset
%p
    = "To reset your password for your #{ @site_name } account, follow the link below:"
= link_to 'Reset Password', edit_password_reset_url( @user.reset_token, :email => @user.email )
%p
    The link will expire two hours from the time this email was sent.
%p
    If you did not request to reset your password, please ignore this email and your password will stay as it is.